      "score": 1,
      "review_title": "Dont play this",
      "review_description": "I got on with my friend rowan because the game looked cool. Played it for about 15 minutes because the game is un-optimized and is very laggy. Its way to dark and I already found a hole in the map thinking I needed to go there since it was so dark in tutorial. I did find the light but it barely works. Volcano for me didnt load it whatsoever and all the monsters and their ai was dysfunctional. They were either stuck on candy cains, in a skull, or doing 360s in the open.",
